      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b>: <em>USH</em></p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 500 gp; <b>Weight</b> 1/2 lb.</p>\r\n<p>This small leather satchel contains various alchemical remedies that treat common maladies caused by exposure to <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Undead\">undead</a>. An undeath aid kit contains 1 dose of each of the following alchemical remedies: <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/herbs-oils-other-substances#TOC-Antiplague\">antiplague</a>, <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/herbs-oils-other-substances#TOC-Antitoxin\">antitoxin</a>, padzahr, soul stimulant, and twitch tonic.</p>\r\n\r\n"
